OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChurch of Scotland to allow
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsame-sex marriages         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Church of Scotland has voted to    
OL,6, allow clergy to conduct same-sex       
OL,7, marriages for the first time.          
OL,9,FMembers of the General Assembly in     
OL,10,FEdinburgh voted to change church law   
OL,11,Ffollowing years of campaigning.        
OL,13,FIt means same-sex couples will be able 
OL,14,Fto marry in church in services         
OL,15,Fconducted by ministers.                
OL,17,FMinisters and deacons will be able to  
OL,18,Fapply to become celebrants of same sex 
OL,19,Fmarriage, but they will not be forced  
OL,20,Fto take part.                          
